ELBERT, Respondent, v. HAEBLER et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by August Elbert against Theodore Haebler and another.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

R. S. Swezey, for appellants. R. B. Honeyman, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
